Place a mass at each &quot;l&quot; end of the box, and time how long it takes
them to gravitate towards one another.  See if they both accelerate
towards the center or if one preferrentially accelerates towards the
other (frame dragging).  See if they mutually gravitate towards one of
the &quot;w&quot; walls (assuming for grins the axis &quot;l&quot; is aligned with the
orbit).

